{"tid":497212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[又來]ios 11.2導致Wi-Fi通話失效？蘋果未回應","createTime":"2017-12-12T13:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T15:41:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9a6d9718184b568b6d450e34a375df293d1e5869","tid":497212,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"根據外媒 MacRumors 的報導，使用 iPhone 的 Sprint 用戶普遍報告說，他們的 iPhone 在安裝了 iOS 11.2 和運營商設置版本 31.0 之後，Wi-Fi 通話無法正常工作。<br />\n<br />\n自本月早些時候發布 iOS 11.2 軟件更新以來，網路上已經出現了數百起投訴，包括 Sprint、蘋果支持社區、推特和 Reddit 等等。所有支持 Wi-Fi 通話的 iPhone 機型似乎都受到了影響，從 iPhone 6 到 iPhone 8 Plus 等。<br />\n<br />\n　　目前還不清楚這一問題是由 iOS 11.2 還是更新後的運營商設置引起的，後者支持 Wi-Fi 通話和 VoLTE 等功能。AT&amp;T、Verizon 和 T-Mobile 的用戶則沒有受到影響，這表明這是一個 Sprint 特有的問題。<br />\n<br />\n　　許多受影響的客戶已經完成了基本的故障排除，比如重置 iPhone 的網路設置，或者乾脆重啟設備，但似乎沒有一個解決方案在 iOS 11.2 系統上是可行的。作為臨時的解決方案，一些用戶已經降級至 iOS 11.1.2，併發現 Wi-Fi 通話再次恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://new.qq.com/omn/20171212A07Z0F.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Fomn%2F20171212A07Z0F.html&d=d8xo9qgt%2FdGmG2m6pAbXi%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=451cb1da\" target=\"_blank\">http://new.qq.com/omn/20171212A07Z0F.html</a>"},{"pid":"eebf30680dc5a19579c9b228454c39b06023819d","tid":497212,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987ddf0cd464c7231a5ce2bed227a96a4a26c5f6","tid":497212,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:37:54.000Z","msg":"呢度無icon玩架"},{"pid":"1cf2e336fc54d5f13ed43e32c62c1da3293d159c","tid":497212,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:49:42.000Z","msg":"次次都即刻更新，好彩今次無啫"},{"pid":"fbbdaad3a8a4697478acdf8e0c1c9b59a2792d22","tid":497212,"uid":17738,"like":0,"